  <body>
    <sec sec-type="">
      <title>Main Text</title>
      <p>In preparation of the manuscript (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B1953300">Fleming et al. 2015</xref>) the authors incorrectly misspelled the patronym dedicated to Jose Mario Moraga. Therefore Based on Art. 32.5.1.1 of the International Code of Zoological Nomenclature (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B1833938">International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature 1999</xref>), and considering the etymology of the species we hereby act to correct the incorrect original misspelling of the name <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Trigonospila</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">josemariamoragai</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Fleming &amp; Wood, 2015, to the correct spelling <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Trigonospila</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">josemariomoragai</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Fleming &amp; Wood, 2015.  All details pertaining to original date of publication and original pagination remain the same.</p>
    </sec>
